# WA Gateway — Baileys + Docker

REST API gateway untuk WhatsApp menggunakan library Baileys, dikemas dalam Docker. Mendukung **multi-session** dengan **round-robin rotator** otomatis.

---

## Fitur

- ✅ Multi-session (lebih dari 1 nomor WA)
- 🔄 Round-robin rotator — pesan dikirim bergantian antar nomor
- 🔁 Auto-reconnect dengan exponential backoff + force QR regenerate
- 📱 QR Scanner di browser (`/scan`)
- 🔔 Webhook outgoing dengan HMAC signature
- 🔑 API Key authentication
- 🛡️ Rate limiting + Helmet security headers + CORS
- 🐳 Docker ready dengan session persisten

---

## Struktur Project

```
wa-gateway/
├── src/
│   ├── index.js                  # Entry point, setup Express
│   ├── handlers/
│   │   ├── whatsapp.js           # WhatsApp client per sesi (Baileys)
│   │   └── session-manager.js   # Kelola semua sesi + round-robin
│   ├── middleware/
│   │   └── auth.js               # API key authentication
│   ├── routes/
│   │   ├── message.js            # Endpoint kirim pesan
│   │   ├── session.js            # Endpoint manajemen multi-sesi
│   │   ├── qr-page.js            # Halaman QR di browser
│   │   └── webhook.js            # Endpoint konfigurasi webhook
│   └── utils/
│       ├── logger.js             # Logger (pino)
│       └── webhook.js            # Helper kirim webhook
├── sessions/                     # Folder session Baileys (di-volume)
├── .env.example
├── Dockerfile
├── docker-compose.yml
└── package.json
```

---

## Setup & Deployment

### 1. Konfigurasi environment

```bash
cp .env.example .env
nano .env
```

Isi minimal:

```env
API_KEY=your-secret-api-key-here
SESSIONS=nomor1,nomor2        # nama sesi, bebas — pisah koma
```

### 2. Build dan jalankan

```bash
docker compose up -d --build
```

### 3. Scan QR Code

Buka browser, akses halaman semua sesi:

```
http://localhost:3000/scan
```

Scan per sesi:

```
http://localhost:3000/scan/nomor1
http://localhost:3000/scan/nomor2
```

Halaman akan **auto-refresh** setiap 30 detik selama menunggu scan.

---

## API Endpoints

### Public (tanpa auth)

| Method | Endpoint          | Deskripsi                        |
|--------|-------------------|----------------------------------|
| GET    | `/health`         | Health check + status semua sesi |
| GET    | `/scan`           | Halaman QR semua sesi (browser)  |
| GET    | `/scan/:sessionId`| Halaman QR sesi tertentu         |

### Protected — butuh header `X-API-Key: <your-key>`

#### Session

| Method | Endpoint                        | Deskripsi                    |
|--------|---------------------------------|------------------------------|
| GET    | `/api/session`                  | List semua sesi              |
| POST   | `/api/session/add`              | Tambah sesi baru             |
| GET    | `/api/session/:sessionId/status`| Status sesi tertentu         |
| DELETE | `/api/session/:sessionId`       | Hapus sesi                   |

#### Message

| Method | Endpoint                       | Deskripsi                         |
|--------|--------------------------------|-----------------------------------|
| POST   | `/api/message/send-text`       | Kirim pesan teks                  |
| POST   | `/api/message/send-image`      | Kirim gambar (URL atau base64)    |
| POST   | `/api/message/send-document`   | Kirim dokumen/file                |
| POST   | `/api/message/check-number`    | Cek nomor terdaftar di WA         |

> Semua endpoint message mendukung field opsional `sessionId`. Jika tidak diisi, otomatis **round-robin**.

#### Webhook

| Method | Endpoint               | Deskripsi                    |
|--------|------------------------|------------------------------|
| POST   | `/api/webhook/set`     | Set URL webhook              |
| GET    | `/api/webhook/config`  | Lihat konfigurasi webhook    |
| DELETE | `/api/webhook/remove`  | Hapus webhook                |

---

## Contoh Request

### Tambah Sesi Baru

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/session/add \
  -H "X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"sessionId": "nomor1"}'
```

### Kirim Teks — Round-Robin Otomatis

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/message/send-text \
  -H "X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"phone": "6281234567890", "message": "Halo dari WA Gateway!"}'
```

Response menyertakan sesi yang digunakan:

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Pesan berhasil dikirim",
  "data": {
    "messageId": "3EB0xxxxxxxxxxxxxx",
    "to": "6281234567890",
    "sentVia": "nomor1"
  }
}
```

### Kirim Teks — Pakai Sesi Spesifik

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/message/send-text \
  -H "X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"phone": "6281234567890", "message": "Halo!", "sessionId": "nomor2"}'
```

### Kirim Gambar dari URL

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/message/send-image \
  -H "X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "phone": "6281234567890",
    "image": "https://example.com/gambar.jpg",
    "caption": "Caption gambar"
  }'
```

### Set Webhook

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/webhook/set \
  -H "X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "url": "https://your-app.com/wa-webhook",
    "events": ["message.received", "session.connected"],
    "secret": "webhook-secret-optional"
  }'
```

### Payload Webhook (event: message.received)

```json
{
  "event": "message.received",
  "timestamp": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
  "data": {
    "sessionId": "nomor1",
    "messageId": "ABCD1234",
    "from": "6281234567890@s.whatsapp.net",
    "fromMe": false,
    "isGroup": false,
    "pushName": "Nama Pengirim",
    "messageType": "conversation",
    "body": "Isi pesan",
    "timestamp": 1704067200
  }
}
```

---

## Konfigurasi `.env`

```env
# Server
PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=production

# Auth — wajib diisi
API_KEY=your-secret-api-key-here

# Sesi — nama bebas, pisah koma
# Folder session akan dibuat otomatis di sessions/<nama>
SESSIONS=nomor1,nomor2,nomor3

# WhatsApp
SESSION_PATH=./sessions
MAX_RECONNECT=0        # 0 = unlimited reconnect
MARK_ONLINE=false      # true = muncul online di WA

# Security
CORS_ORIGIN=*          # domain yang diizinkan, * = semua
RATE_LIMIT=60          # maks request per menit per IP

# Logging
LOG_LEVEL=info
BAILEYS_LOG_LEVEL=silent
```

---

## Perilaku Reconnect

| Kondisi | Perilaku |
|---|---|
| Internet mati sementara | Reconnect otomatis, backoff 2s → 4s → 8s → ... → 30s |
| WA server restart | Reconnect langsung tanpa delay |
| QR tidak muncul > 60 detik | Force hapus auth + generate QR baru |
| Max reconnect tercapai | Force hapus auth + mulai dari awal |
| HP di-logout dari WA | Tidak reconnect — scan QR ulang di `/scan/:sessionId` |
| Berhasil connect ulang | Counter reconnect direset ke 0 |
| Keepalive | Ping ke WA server setiap 25 detik |

---

## Format Nomor

| Input | Hasil |
|---|---|
| `6281234567890` | ✅ Benar |
| `081234567890` | ✅ Otomatis dikonversi |
| `+6281234567890` | ✅ Otomatis dikonversi |
| `120363xxxxxxxx@g.us` | ✅ Untuk kirim ke grup |

---

## Docker Commands

```bash
# Jalankan
docker compose up -d --build

# Lihat log semua
docker compose logs -f

# Lihat log satu container
docker compose logs -f wa-gateway

# Restart
docker compose restart wa-gateway

# Stop
docker compose down

# Reset sesi tertentu (scan ulang)
docker compose down
docker run --rm -v wa-gateway_wa_sessions:/data alpine rm -rf /data/nomor1
docker compose up -d

# Reset semua sesi
docker volume rm wa-gateway_wa_sessions
docker compose up -d --build
```

---

## Webhook Events

| Event | Kapan dikirim |
|---|---|
| `session.qr`           | QR baru tersedia |
| `session.connected`    | Sesi berhasil terhubung |
| `session.disconnected` | Sesi terputus |
| `message.received`     | Pesan masuk diterima |
| `message.status`       | Status pesan berubah (delivered, read) |

Gunakan `"events": ["*"]` untuk subscribe semua event.